  "detailed_description": "<strong>Strike Team Delta</strong> is a 1-4 player online co-op zombie horror. Complete tasks and puzzles to restore the fate of humanity.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Don't forget to wishlist!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892910/extras/5dbcb663a709c5c7f7db0c28bc1ae50c.poster.avif?t=1722084316\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892910/extras/5dbcb663a709c5c7f7db0c28bc1ae50c.webm?t=1722084316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892910/extras/5dbcb663a709c5c7f7db0c28bc1ae50c.mp4?t=1722084316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Are you good enough for the delta team?</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Online Co-Op</strong><br>Play with up to 4 friends and you all must work together to retrieve the objective and survive.<br></li><li><strong>Replayability</strong><br>In Strike Team Delta, each playthrough is different, with random spawns ensuring you have a different experience every time.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892910/extras/922a7b371fd50063dce84868ec222ae0.avif?t=1722084316\" width=600 height=340 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weapon Customisation</h2>Build your guns the way you want them!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892910/extras/7e7eccd4563339868eb074907c806109.poster.avif?t=1722084316\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892910/extras/7e7eccd4563339868eb074907c806109.webm?t=1722084316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892910/extras/7e7eccd4563339868eb074907c806109.mp4?t=1722084316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Character Customisation</h2>Choose what gear to wear into battle<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892910/extras/ef13d227647ea979893dcfa111245598.poster.avif?t=1722084316\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892910/extras/ef13d227647ea979893dcfa111245598.webm?t=1722084316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892910/extras/ef13d227647ea979893dcfa111245598.mp4?t=1722084316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Saving humanity</h2>Not only is your goal to survive, but you will also need to retrieve the objective you have been sent to get<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Immersive Gameplay</h2>Strike Team Delta is powered by Unreal Engine 5 ensuring the highest quality graphics for the most immersive horror experience possible.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892910/extras/bafcbf24e2fac630ebe3acc1d1d4e8bd.avif?t=1722084316\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Modding Support</strong><br>It is one of the early plans to enable modding support for the community to build any epic mission they desire!<br></li><li><strong>Player Progression</strong><br>You should see player progression to unlock attachments, player skins, and weapon skins soon<br></li><li><strong>Procedural animations</strong><br>Procedural animations for reloads, firing, and grips are all coming very soon!<br></li><li><strong>More Maps & Missions</strong><br>I will be adding a few more maps and missions to the base game before unleashing the modding community.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Strike Team Delta</strong> is a 1-4 player online co-op zombie horror. Complete tasks and puzzles to restore the fate of humanity.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Don't forget to wishlist!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892910/extras/5dbcb663a709c5c7f7db0c28bc1ae50c.poster.avif?t=1722084316\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892910/extras/5dbcb663a709c5c7f7db0c28bc1ae50c.webm?t=1722084316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892910/extras/5dbcb663a709c5c7f7db0c28bc1ae50c.mp4?t=1722084316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Are you good enough for the delta team?</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Online Co-Op</strong><br>Play with up to 4 friends and you all must work together to retrieve the objective and survive.<br></li><li><strong>Replayability</strong><br>In Strike Team Delta, each playthrough is different, with random spawns ensuring you have a different experience every time.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892910/extras/922a7b371fd50063dce84868ec222ae0.avif?t=1722084316\" width=600 height=340 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weapon Customisation</h2>Build your guns the way you want them!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892910/extras/7e7eccd4563339868eb074907c806109.poster.avif?t=1722084316\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892910/extras/7e7eccd4563339868eb074907c806109.webm?t=1722084316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://sha